text: Jakup Krasniqi (born 1 January 1951) is a Kosovar politician. He was the Acting President of Kosovo twice between September 2010 to February 2011 and again in April 2011. He was Chairman of the Assembly of Kosovo between 2007 and 2014. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Kosovo
title: Jakup Krasniqi
